{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"5305b","heading":"Educational outreach program","label":"5305b Educational outreach program","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s5305b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/ch73","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs5305b","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"In general","label":"a In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s5305b/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s5305b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs5305b%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Not later than 180 days after , the Secretary shall develop and implement an educational outreach program in the United States for the conservation of rhinoceros and tiger species.October 30, 1998","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Guidelines","label":"b Guidelines","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s5305b/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s5305b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs5305b%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary shall publish in the Federal Register guidelines for the program.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Contents","label":"c Contents","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s5305b/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s5305b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs5305b%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s5305b/c/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s5305b/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs5305b%2Fc%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"laws protecting rhinoceros and tiger species, in particular laws prohibiting trade in products containing, or labeled or advertised as containing, their parts;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s5305b/c/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s5305b/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs5305b%2Fc%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"use of traditional medicines that contain parts or products of rhinoceros and tiger species, health risks associated with their use, and available alternatives to the medicines; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s5305b/c/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s5305b/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs5305b%2Fc%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the status of rhinoceros and tiger species and the reasons for protecting the species.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}
